Overview

Demonstrates external lead ingestion through the Lead Operating System using the external intake expansion architecture.

The recording validates source mapping, intake routing, governance tracking, and successful downstream processing of externally originated records.

Recording Objectives

Demonstrate:

External source submission

External intake mapping

Lead routing

Pipeline processing

Campaign activation

Governance updates

Final completion
